<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>" الله أكبر <span class="c1">". فيسجد "</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
